{"tid":2230755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港歷史博物館　「香港故事」　學者：被要求做「中港邊界融合」","createTime":"2020-10-05T06:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:01:19.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"273cf3fffe3874673b418e5ddb4635dffa2c7781","tid":2230755,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jackyu1230/posts/891641167908889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjackyu1230%2Fposts%2F891641167908889&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGAZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=fd4417a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jackyu1230/posts/891641167908889</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：余震宇 Jacky Yu<br />\n<br />\n17:18 更新: 原來當年館方還要求寫「人工島」，不曉得是否與「明日大嶼」有關。不過2018年，施政報告就提到「明日大嶼」的計劃了。<br />\n<br />\n香港歷史博物館常設展覽《香港故事》即將關閉，進行更新工程，並於2022年完成。<br />\n<br />\n2018年，香港歷史博物館曾經找本人洽談更新內容，打算將海岸線系列著作加入《新香港故事》\b，我也曾經親自與館方會面。<br />\n<br />\n不過館方開列的內容有點奇怪，不僅要求本人準備海岸線的資料，也要求完成「中港邊界融合」的部份。<br />\n<br />\n真奇怪，我不是「中港邊界融合」的專家，對「中港邊界」沒研究，我要求不做這部份。<br />\n<br />\n怎料，不久就有電話告訴我：「我們不用你的幫忙了。」<br />\n<br />\n也奇怪，邀請就有邀請信，踢你走就只有一通電話。<br />\n<br />\n這是香港。"},{"pid":"70a75be92644444a4e3a2f745a4e639bb5810fe8","tid":2230755,"uid":83251,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"中港市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fe1af441cc191c7460c367eb621b44b419a0e3","tid":2230755,"uid":167509,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"歷史都fake news<br />\n下一代會以為強國幫香港"},{"pid":"32674dc32b10f6e39ee5f0d68e9ffc2bb6387c63","tid":2230755,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"全撚部政治任務"},{"pid":"aa844b0d8462644738cabd9e87f3c9342dadc54b","tid":2230755,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"食屎啦學者"},{"pid":"42210f80afa2fda228a225d20aeba44ae52a5